long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tired of tediously searching for building codes? Overwhelmed by the major code updates? 

Introducing StructWise: Your AI assistant for structural codes, standards and guidances. 

Let StructWise help your code research by providing instant access to accurate and latest building codes at your finger tips. Simply ask your questions like you would to ChatGPT, except StructWise is specifically trained to understand the nuance of structural engineering!

Say goodbye to manual searches and hello to efficiency with StructWise!




Disclaimer:

StructWise aims to enhance access to publications, but does not guarantee absolute accuracy. Users must verify information and use it at their own risk. StructWise is not liable for errors or omissions. The AI assistant provides glimpses and rephrased summaries of publications, respecting copyright laws. It does not reproduce or redistribute copyrighted content in full. Users are responsible for ensuring their use complies with applicable copyright regulations.

By using the AI assistant, users agree to this disclaimer. StructWise may modify this disclaimer without notice.
